text: The Kop van Overijssel (literally in English: Head of Overijssel) is a region in the north of the province of Overijssel, the Netherlands. It consists of the municipality of Steenwijkerland and three municipalities which are also considered being part of the region of Salland: Kampen, Staphorst, and Zwartewaterland. == Related pages == * Salland * Twente == References == * Plaatsengids.nl Category:Regions of the Netherlands
title: Kop van Overijssel
